7
00:01:05,975 --> 00:01:11,763
The Buddha uses the word which translates as the world, loke.

8
00:01:11,784 --> 00:01:16,390
He says in this world there is this dukkha and the end of it.

9
00:01:17,111 --> 00:01:26,063
So dukkha is one of these very difficult words to translate because it has ideas which just doesn't make sense to us in terms of the word suffering

10
