Aversion is easy to get because aversion immediately distances the object.

17
00:02:33,134 --> 00:02:33,836
It makes it an enemy.

18
00:02:33,855 --> 00:02:34,717
You want to push it away.

19
00:02:35,296 --> 00:02:41,062
So one is not aware of any feelings of aversion, fear, all that sort of stuff.

20
00:02:41,081 --> 00:02:44,344
When it comes to indulgence, it's a close marriage.

21
00:02:45,006 --> 00:02:47,328
They're very difficult to distinguish.

22
00:02:48,908 --> 00:02:50,189
Even so, distinguish we must.

23
00:02:51,812 --> 00:02:54,454
So this word dukkha is

24
