00:16:26,695 --> 00:16:55,284
if you were to just stop a human being and slice down right down there at that moment in time you get this congregation this aggregation of things but when it's in process then it becomes dependence origination the whole process of dependence origination and the point of interest for us is that point where the five khandhas these five groups have actually

