at that point, you see, there's a habit of just trying to grasp the object trying to hold it, trying to develop it and there's that desire there see, nothing's happened at that point that's why it manifests as an intention it manifests as a desire, as an intention and I was saying that if we can just remain at that point

147
00:19:21,705 --> 00:19:39,785
to hold that point, to hover within that point, and recognize that movement, that desire, as being unwholesome, and just wait for the energy of that to dissipate, to just blow itself out, we're destroying that conditioning.

